issue.body:
***Note**: This issue was originally created as [ARROW-17786](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ARROW-17786). Please see the [migration documentation](https://gist.github.com/toddfarmer/12aa88361532d21902818a6044fda4c3) for further details.*

### Original Issue Description:
Add "case 3" to offer CSV Read support:
```java

case 0:
  return std::make_shared<arrow::dataset::ParquetFileFormat>();
case 1:
  return std::make_shared<arrow::dataset::IpcFileFormat>();
case 2:
  return std::make_shared<arrow::dataset::OrcFileFormat>();
case 3:
  return std::make_shared<arrow::dataset::CsvFileFormat>(); 
```
